description: We are a Game Changing Hospitality and event planning company. Our goal is to bring not only our delicious brand of BBQ but a unique “Game Changing” experience to your next tailgate, house party, corporate event, fundraiser or any other event you can dream up. We bring our BBQ and delicious sides on our state of the art trailer with satellite TV and capacity to feed thousands. But that’s not all! We also bring our expertise, providing an amazing experience with fun and exciting staff that not only get the party going but help you create a true tailgating experience.
name: Tailgater Toby NOVA
